    • A

      private void A(String fname, String lname, String date, String major, int creditsCompleted)
      Adds student to roster with the following restrictions:
      • Any date of birth that is not a valid calendar date
      • The date of birth is today or a future date
      • A student who is less than 16 years old
      • The major doesnâ€™t exist
      • The student is in the roster already
      • Negative number of credit completed
      Parameters:
      fname - first name to add to profile.
      lname - last name to add to profile.
      date - date of birth to add to profile.
      major - major to add to student object.
      creditsCompleted - credits completed to add to student object.

    • R

      private void R(String fname, String lname, String date)
      Removes the specified student from the roster. Rejects if the user is removing a student who is not in the roster.
      Parameters:
      fname - first name to be removed from the roster.
      lname - last name to be removed from the roster.
      date - date of birth to be removed from the roster.
